00:28:08,390 --> 00:28:11,340
I don't know anything about a secret formula.

335
00:28:11,340 --> 00:28:14,170
It's better that you talk to Secretary Zhou.

336
00:28:17,500 --> 00:28:20,050
Since this is the case,

337
00:28:20,050 --> 00:28:22,930
