340
00:28:51,120 --> 00:28:53,990
Cai Hong, don't worry.

341
00:28:53,990 --> 00:28:57,800
Don't be nervous. What you should do is take a deep breath.

342
00:29:01,040 --> 00:29:05,170
Do not add your own distress to this trying time.

343
00:29:05,170 --> 00:29:07,500
Don't worry.

344
00:29:07,500 --> 00:29:09,350
Leave everything to me.

345
00:29:13,500 --> 00:29:16,270
<i>Look. How could they sell it?</i>

346
00:29:16,270 --> 00:29:18,540
<i>-How did it come to this? <br> -Wouldn't we be losing money? <br> -Precisely.</i>

347
00:29:18,580 --> 00:29:20,980
<i>How much is it going to cost?</i>

348
00:29:20,980 --> 00:29:22,820
<i>How much could they get from the sale?</i>

349
00:29:22,820 --> 00:29:25,860
<i>I never imagined that Ling Long would be in this state today.</i>

