00:29:25,860 --> 00:29:27,490
<i>Who doesn't know about this?</i>

351
00:29:27,490 --> 00:29:29,630
- Everyone is here. <br>- Cai Hong is here.

352
00:29:30,800 --> 00:29:34,270
So far only one company, Yao Sheng, is here.

353
00:29:36,130 --> 00:29:39,890
Let's talk while we wait.

354
00:29:41,700 --> 00:29:44,310
Dear Sir, Miss Wu is here.

355
00:29:44,310 --> 00:29:46,210
Can we start now?

356
00:29:56,850 --> 00:29:58,640
It's you.

357
00:30:00,670 --> 00:30:03,060
You are Wu Hong Da's daughter?

358
00:30:08,150 --> 00:30:10,460
