359
00:30:11,860 --> 00:30:13,590
You both know each other?

360
00:30:16,110 --> 00:30:18,710
It can be considered so.

361
00:30:18,710 --> 00:30:21,910
Let's start now. We invited the shareholders here today

362
00:30:21,910 --> 00:30:24,530
and also those who are interested in buying the company.

363
00:30:24,530 --> 00:30:27,400
We are here to discuss the matter about Ling Long.

364
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:31,140
The sale agreement that I've drafted, I believe this gentleman has already seen it.

365
00:30:31,140 --> 00:30:33,560
I wonder what is your opinion.

366
00:30:33,560 --> 00:30:37,590
My offer, is five percent of your selling price.

367
00:30:37,590 --> 00:30:40,410
Five percent? Are you kidding?

368
00:30:40,410 --> 00:30:42,210
This is outrageous!

369
00:30:42,210 --> 00:30:45,630
