370
00:30:45,630 --> 00:30:48,540
- This is our blood, sweat and tears... <br>- Everyone, stay calm.

371
00:30:52,210 --> 00:30:55,460
This gentleman... <br> After all, our Ling Long is a time-honored brand.

372
00:30:55,460 --> 00:30:57,710
