384
00:31:37,050 --> 00:31:39,200
I should say this.

385
00:31:39,200 --> 00:31:42,100
No one would dare to make an offer.

386
00:31:42,100 --> 00:31:45,800
If you don't believe me, you can ask around.

387
00:31:45,800 --> 00:31:48,970
I stated it very clearly. Today's five percent

388
00:31:48,970 --> 00:31:52,020
