389
00:31:52,020 --> 00:31:54,570
Starting from now, it will be less one percent every day.

390
00:31:54,570 --> 00:31:57,710
Everyone, make your decision.

391
00:31:57,710 --> 00:32:01,210
What should we do?

392
00:32:01,210 --> 00:32:02,510
Make it five percent then.

393
00:32:02,520 --> 00:32:04,990
Compared to being bankrupt, I support the sale.

394
00:32:04,990 --> 00:32:07,440
He is the only one offering us silver anyway. <br><i>(silver was a common currency in this period).</i>

395
00:32:07,440 --> 00:32:10,800
