396
00:32:10,800 --> 00:32:13,220
You don't agree? Even if you don't, we should sell it.

397
00:32:13,220 --> 00:32:15,130
If you don't sell it, we will be paupers.

398
00:32:15,130 --> 00:32:18,930
That's right. Even if we total up all our shares, it's still not enough.

399
00:32:18,930 --> 00:32:22,970
Don't talk to her anymore. What does she know?

400
00:32:22,970 --> 00:32:26,620
Everyone, don't be anxious first.

401
00:32:26,620 --> 00:32:29,220
The Wu family is still the biggest shareholder of Ling Long.

402
00:32:29,220 --> 00:32:32,130
Let's listen to Miss Wu's views.

403
00:32:32,130 --> 00:32:34,870
Give her some time to consider.

404
00:32:34,870 --> 00:32:36,650
What do you think?

405
00:32:37,970 --> 00:32:39,850
<i>Let's just sell it.</i>

406
00:32:39,850 --> 00:32:43,130
<i>What should we do if we don't sell it? This is happening too fast.</i>

407
00:32:43,130 --> 00:32:45,870
<i>How much is it worth?</i>

408
00:33:12,690 --> 00:33:15,830
